# Word Concatenation Program
This program asks the user to enter two words and then prints the two words combined into one string.

# Features
- Asks the user for a first word
- Asks the user for a second word
- Concatenates both words
- Displays the combined result

# How to use
Run the program and enter two words when prompted.
The program will print the two words joined together.




# Learning Purpose
This project was created as part of my backend engineering practice.
The goal was to improve my skills in Python, user input handling, strings, and basic concatenation.
